betterquesting.name: Blast Furnace
betterquesting.desc: Now that you have the coke dust its time to bring it all together in the construction of a Blast furnace.

betterquesting.name: Coke Oven
betterquesting.desc: In order to fortify iron into something a bit more durable you'll first need a better source of carbon. Construct a coke oven.

betterquesting.name: Embers of New Power
betterquesting.desc: Deep within the earth an intangible energy permeates the bedrock. Construct something to harness this energy.

betterquesting.name: Tinkers Tonstruct
betterquesting.desc: Now's a good time to construct a Smeltery!

betterquesting.name: Bucketing 101!
betterquesting.desc: Buckets with all sorts of liquids. Will you be the bucket master?

betterquesting.name: So begins the Grind
betterquesting.desc: Construct a Grindstone from Applied Energistics 2 to turn ore into dust for smelting.

betterquesting.name: Plates and Wires and Things
betterquesting.desc: The metal former from IC2 is a versitile machine that can create wires, or plates, much cheaper than doing it manually. It's slow at first so be sure to invest in overclockers later!

betterquesting.name: Powering the Future
betterquesting.desc: A basic ic2 coal generator should be enough to get you started.

betterquesting.name: Reinforced Stone
betterquesting.desc: Placing Cf powder into a block of water seems to make some strange fluid... perhaps you should craft some iron scaffolding to spray it on...

betterquesting.name: Cf Powder
betterquesting.desc: Sometimes you just want to use anything to build. Doesn't have to be pretty!

betterquesting.name: Hammering out the Details
betterquesting.desc: Now that you've got some creosote, make an engineer's hammer. This will allow you to make plates and dusts, at a moderate efficieny loss compared to machines of course.

betterquesting.name: Keep on Squeezing
betterquesting.desc: Using a forestry squeezer should allow you to make enough seed oil to inefficiently produce some creosote for an engineering or IC2 Hammer to make plates.

betterquesting.name: Thermionics
betterquesting.desc: Electron tubes are a key ingredient in some of the machinery you'll soon be working with. Build a thermionic fabricator to facilitate this.

betterquesting.name: EU -> Universal Energy!
betterquesting.desc: The Mekanism energy cube can convert EU to RF and RF to EU, this will act as a bridge between power systems. Keep in mind the Mek energy cube starts at a t2 power source and goes up with higher tier mek cubes. You'll need a transformer for t1 EU Machines.

betterquesting.name: Atomic Reconstructor
betterquesting.desc: Advancing your understand of energy and their systems has led you to a revolutionary breakthrough. The atomic reconstructor can take mundane items and transform them into a completely new type of matter.

betterquesting.name: Resonator
betterquesting.desc: The resonator seems to be able to inject a redstone frequency that resonates with the void into materials to produce a range of useful items.

betterquesting.name: Better than Steel
betterquesting.desc: Now that you've extracted the titanium you'll need to take it back to the blast furnace.

betterquesting.name: The Byproducts of Progress
betterquesting.desc: As strong as steel is, you have found trace amounts of something even strong within aluminum deposits. Construct a crusher to break the ore down and extract titanium byproducts.

betterquesting.name: A story about Hank
betterquesting.desc: A long time ago there was a man named Hank. Hank liked to setup quarries in the overworld. One day Hank wasn't paying attention and quarried someones base. Hank got banned. Don't be hank. Quarry responsibly

betterquesting.name: Macerating Ores
betterquesting.desc: By macerating ores you can increase the yield each ore will provide.

betterquesting.name: Forging better tools
betterquesting.desc: A Tinker's toolforge should now be within your reach. Hammer Time!

betterquesting.name: Compressors
betterquesting.desc: Turning base items into blocks requires quite a bit more pressure than you can muster on your own. A compressor will aid in this.

betterquesting.name: Ash of Arcane power
betterquesting.desc: To create a super rich soil for imbuing radiant magics into plants you'll need a very magic rich type of soil. Create Ash by burning dirt in a cinder plinth.

betterquesting.name: The End of the World
betterquesting.desc: Beyond the edges of the overworld, on the edge of the void itself is a dimension filled with dark shadow creatures and untold treasures both magical and mundane. Legends speaks of a far away stronghold where a portal to such a place exists, but you've elected to take a short cut and construct an artificial portal.

betterquesting.name: Flickers of Magic
betterquesting.desc: Curious magical sprites seem to flicker about throughout the world. Each seems to have some special attunement to the magic world. Perhaps building a trap and providing it with an etherium source may provide a method of capturing them.

betterquesting.name: Flower Power
betterquesting.desc: With the help of the Ember infused ash you've devised a manner of fertilizer that may allow magic bearing flowers to grow. Use it were plants normally grow and reap your rewards.

betterquesting.name: Roots Altar
betterquesting.desc: Using the foundation of runestones you can focus the natural energies of the earth into a new altar. Construct this to proceed.

betterquesting.name: The root of more power
betterquesting.desc: To create an attunement with the natural world some livingrock combined with precious gems may work to create runestones as a base of power.

betterquesting.name: Magic, Refined.
betterquesting.desc: With the strange properties of Psi metal and the otherworldy runes you've managed to weave a new altar that focuses magics into new ways. The essence refiner will burn etherium and material components to create essences.

betterquesting.name: Casting Assist!
betterquesting.desc: The power of the mind in known to be incredible, harnessing it has never been easy... until now. By of of the all new patented "Casting Assist Decice" You too can now focus and direct this energy. Your own creativity may be all that limits you here.

betterquesting.name: Leaves from another world
betterquesting.desc: Using this new nature altar you've found a way to summon creatures of magic from beyond this world. Summon some sprites and collect their leaves. You may kill them for it, but it may suit you more to build a mana font and keep them happy so they will continually drop them for you with no future effort.

betterquesting.name: Mana infused Steel
betterquesting.desc: Now that you've unlocked the potential of the new flowers mana flows from them. Focus this mana into a pull and try infusing some of your steel into it.

betterquesting.name: This Daisy Rocks
betterquesting.desc: Proceeding into the ways of magic will require unlocking the potential of the magic infused flowers you've created. A petal apothecary you get you on your way, as well as few other accoutrements.

betterquesting.name: True Power Lies Within
betterquesting.desc: Find a pool of etherium in the world. Place an item frame next to it with a book and watch as the secrets of eternity reveal themselves to you. To truely get started however you're going to need an altar to create your spells.

betterquesting.name: Echos of Draconic Power
betterquesting.desc: Collect Ender Biotite, this material seems to be infused with raw draconic will, useful for a new form of magic!

betterquesting.name: Star Power
betterquesting.desc: By focusing starlight found in various rock crystals around the world onto a crafting table you've found you are able to harness this energy. Use this to create a something that will be even more efficient at channeling this energy for your future needs.

betterquesting.name: Dawning of a New Age
betterquesting.desc: The strange ember energy seems to align itself with gold and copper, perhaps with some tinkering you can devise a new alloy... It may also be possible to melt the copper and gold in a smeltery first and then pipe into the mixer, piping the resultant dawnstown to a casting table and ingot cast seems to work as well.

betterquesting.name: Resonant Stone
betterquesting.desc: Bringing the resonator to bear stoneburnt seems to be a highly useful in the generation of the same type of energyies.

betterquesting.name: Raw Iridium
betterquesting.desc: This rare material seems to be found in the roof of the nether, although far too rare to be obtained reliably. The molecular transformer seems to be capable of producing the stuff though, if you can keep up with the power cost.

betterquesting.name: Molecular Transformation
betterquesting.desc: Building on the ideals of the Atomic reconstructor you've determined a much more power version. The molecular transformer seems capable of turning vast amounts of energy into useful materials.

betterquesting.name: Induction Power
betterquesting.desc: Many unique alloys and glasses can be made in an induction smelter. Some which you speculate may enable a new form of super fast data transfer.

betterquesting.name: Infusing Metals
betterquesting.desc: R&D has lead you to the development of an idea to infuse metals with energetic materials. By constructing an energetic infuser you believe you may be able to impart some qualities of carbon, redstone, diamond and perhaps others into metals directly.

betterquesting.name: Highspeed Data Storage
betterquesting.desc: Finally a monumental breakthrough. With all the materials you have now experimented with you've discovered a method of near superluminal data transformation and transmission. An applied energistics network will help facilitate your future work.

betterquesting.name: Restonia
betterquesting.desc: A strange new material from atomic reconstruction of redstone, imagine what uses it may have...

betterquesting.name: Arc to the Future
betterquesting.desc: Utilizing some of the newer metals you realize you can create powerful alloys if only you could generate enough heat and currently quickly enough. An Arc furnace should do this job nicely. Construct an arc furnace and the electrodes.

betterquesting.name: Sunnarium
betterquesting.desc: Raw energy condensed into glowing stones from the nether yield a highly energetic form of light producing alloy. Sunnarium seems to have a highly versatile nature.

betterquesting.name: Orbital Mining Platform
betterquesting.desc: Uninspected mineral ores and dilithium are some of the most rare materials you can find. Your research as pointed you towards desining a new orbital mining platform that should be capable of extracting these and many other ores from a planetary space station in orbit around any planet. Create a space stationa nd orbital Mining platform to exploit these resources.

betterquesting.name: To The Moon
betterquesting.desc: You're going to need a more potent fuel source, theoretical models predict the existence of a dilithium crystaline structure. Unfortunately no one has located this on earth. Build a ship to take you to the moon to search for some!

betterquesting.name: Osmiridium
betterquesting.desc: By re-melting and then alloying osmium and iridium you can create a much more useful alloy. You'll need this is the creation of more advanced machinery.

betterquesting.name: More human than human
betterquesting.desc: Bringing the full technological advancements at your disposal to bear on your own mortality, you have created a method of replacing parts of yourself with cybernetic improvements.

betterquesting.name: A Dire Situtation....
betterquesting.desc: You're going to need a bigger crafting table for what you have in mind. Much Bigger.

betterquesting.name: When They are One...
betterquesting.desc: By combining your experiences with transmutation magics and raw industrilized power of mechanical and otherworldy engineering you have devised a material more potent than any before. You forsee near infinite uses for this.

betterquesting.name: Creative Builder's Wand
betterquesting.desc: Somes you just need to place MOAR BLOCKS!

betterquesting.name: Unbreakable, Insatiable Tinkers
betterquesting.desc: Create a creative upgrade modifier for your gear, grants an additional modifier!

betterquesting.name: Creative Screening
betterquesting.desc: Screens, everywhere! And no controllers or powers needed.

betterquesting.name: Infinity Fluid Producer
betterquesting.desc: So many Possibilities... UU Matter Lake? Lava filled Ravines, or how about your own coffee waterfall.

betterquesting.name: Ultimate Alchemy
betterquesting.desc: The ultimate breakthrough! You've found a way to transmute almost any form of material into another form of matter. Lead to Gold? Child's play, you weave diamonds from dirt!

betterquesting.name: Creative CAD Assembler
betterquesting.desc: Some assembly required, dragon eggs not included.

betterquesting.name: Mana, Guilt Free!
betterquesting.desc: Bringing together all you've unlocked a limitless source of mana is within your grasp.... But what will you do with it?

betterquesting.name: It's ALIVE!!!
betterquesting.desc: A near limitless internal power source to power all your cybernetic implants. Ironman may be jealous.
Power is no longer an issue, as is if were by now anyway...

betterquesting.name: UNLIMITED GP... itty bitty space
betterquesting.desc: Unlimited GP Sound nice? The creative mill has you covered.

betterquesting.name: OH No!
betterquesting.desc: There doesn't appear to be anything here. Perhaps the princess is in another castle.  Congratulations, You've beaten the pack. I Hope you're proud of yourself. We're certainly not. Just Kidding. Probably.

betterquesting.name: Cheating with magic.
betterquesting.desc: Utilizing all you've mastered thus far you believe it possible to duplicate the essence of some materials with pure magic. The conjuration catalyst should allow you to double many items using mana.

betterquesting.name: Portal to another world
betterquesting.desc: The lexica botania speaks of the Alfheim, a magical world inhabited by elves. Create an elven gateway so you can barter for their magics.

betterquesting.name: Dark Matter!
betterquesting.desc: Transmutations of untold energy densities have uncovered a completely new form of condensed matter. Dark matter opens up so many new possibilities for you...

betterquesting.name: Gemmed Out
betterquesting.desc: Create Darkmatter Boots

betterquesting.name: Gemmed out Part 3
betterquesting.desc: Create a darkmatter Chestplate.

betterquesting.name: Terra Steel!
betterquesting.desc: By focusing tremendous amounts of mana into mana steel, along with mana infused ender pearls and diamonds you have found a way to make a metal even more deeply infused with mana. This new Terra Steel should be able to withstand the combined stresses of sustaining a gateway to alfheim itself.

betterquesting.name: Runes of Elven Power
betterquesting.desc: By using the starmetal as an altar base you are able to create a suitable platform to infuse mana directly into the inscribed elven runes etched into living rock. These will be useful in stabilizing future magical research.

betterquesting.name: Gemmed out Part 4
betterquesting.desc: Create the Final piece, Dark Matter boots.

betterquesting.name: Star Metal
betterquesting.desc: Your studies have come to a dead end. You cannot seem to find any further way to progress your arcane knowledge on earth. Turning your sights to the skies, or more accurately, to the stars, you realize you may be able to harness the power of starmetal by delving into Astral sorcery.

betterquesting.name: Blood for the Blood God
betterquesting.desc: Using the new biotite you've found a way to warp the spirits of the otherworld into raw will which you infuse with blood. The resulting discovery opens a completely new branch of magical research for you to exploit.

betterquesting.name: Demon Metal
betterquesting.desc: Legend tells of a metal infused with pure evil and the magic of the Nether. In the nether there exists natural wells of lava surrounded by nether bricks inside fortresses. Perhaps throwing a rare metal ingot into one of these may forge the malevolence into a new material.

betterquesting.name: Forged in the fires of hell
betterquesting.desc: After learning to harvest the life essence of living things you've determined it may also be possible to use demonic will to the same end. Construct a hellfire forge to empower your magic with raw demon will.

betterquesting.name: Mana Alchemy
betterquesting.desc: After the messy business of life experimentation you've come up with a more elegant solution. By utilizing the magical nature of mana you can transmute items into other more useful items. Construct an alchemy catalyst to place under a mana pool which will alter it's operations.

betterquesting.name: Infernal Alchemy
betterquesting.desc: Transmutation utilizing the life essence of your slain victims seems tricky. Most experentation left you with a mess. You finally devised a table to work on that can allow reagent to be made. Construct an Alchemy Table.

betterquesting.name: On the wings of an Angel
betterquesting.desc: Pure creative flight!

betterquesting.name: Gemmed Out Part 2
betterquesting.desc: Create a dark matter helmet

betterquesting.name: Bending Time to your will
betterquesting.desc: Using the tremendous potential bound within dark matter you've found a way to alter time itself.

betterquesting.name: Strange Alien Rocks....
betterquesting.desc: You obtained notes on a strange but very rare type of ore. It seems to contain vast amounce of trace minerals, most extremely rare. Obtaining this may prove difficult however. It can allegedly be mined from an orbital platform, although there may be some magical way of also creating it.

betterquesting.name: Sizing up the Elements
betterquesting.desc: To start the proces of refinement, the mineral sizer should suffice to crush the ore into more meaningful shard clusters.

betterquesting.name: Alloyer
betterquesting.desc: Now that you've broken the minerals down you'll need a machine capable of alloying up to 9 different constituent components to create an array of alloying possibilities. The metal alloyer will work for this.

betterquesting.name: Laboratory Expansion
betterquesting.desc: These new rocks seem particularly difficulty to break down. You've devised a series of chemical reactions that should do the trick but you're going to need specialized equipment to produce the nescesary acids.

betterquesting.name: Fuel upgrade
betterquesting.desc: Running these new machines gets expensive in raw materials it seems. Converting them to RF seems to be a good goal.

betterquesting.name: Sticks and Stones
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: Logs and Wands
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: Nuts and Bolts
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: Mastery of All Things
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: RotaryCraft
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: Runes, Rites and Rituals
betterquesting.desc: No description

betterquesting.name: Advanced Alloys
betterquesting.desc: No description
